A private electronic letter (email) sent 

from me to P.Z. Myers with express permission to republish is infringed by
 
the text reposted on the site listed below. Beginning with "While I have  

always deep down been..." and ending with "consequences of that belief".  

P.Z. Myers has permission to repost the letter; the infringing site has no
 
such permission.
